snippet.title: "I Bribed Johnny" Amber Heard Admits She Deserved To Go To Prison
snippet.description:
💙 "I Bribed Johnny" Amber Heard Admits She Deserved To Go To Prison
Amber Heard's career took a U-turn from success and celebrity when she declared herself a victim of violence from her ex-husband, actor Johnny Depp. The media opted to believe Heard despite the lack of evidence, and the major film studios followed suit. As a result of these allegations, Johnny Depp lost some of his most notable roles. You wouldn't believe how Hollywood is now abusing two of their most talented performers!
